The 2026 Artist-in-Residency cohort is supported by The Harkness Foundation for Dance. Save the date for the cohort sharing on June 20 and 21, 2026.

Each resident is in the middle of a co-designed residency — bios and project descriptions will be added to the directory throughout the residency period.
